			Profile
			
			
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Dr.HE,Guang-yu
&nbsp;
BScGeology,ChinaUniversityofGeoscience(Wuhan),1991
MscPetroleumGeology,ChinaUniversityofGeoscience(Wuhan),1995
Ph.D.BasinAnalysisandSimulation,ChinaUniversityofGeoscience(Wuhan),1998
&nbsp;
Dr.HEiscurrentlyanassociateprofessor(since2002)atZhejiangUniversity.&nbsp;Heisalsoanappointedassistantdirector(fornewmaritimeindustriesandengagementwithuniversities)ofZhoushanCity&rsquo;sDevelopmentandReformCommission.
&nbsp;
Hehasbeenworkingasanassistantengineerin(1991&ndash;1993)theDevelopmentOfficeattheGeologicalResearchInstituteofSINOPECHenanOilfieldBranchCompany,aresearchscientist(1998)thenassociateprofessor(2000)atNanjingUniversity.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Hehasbeenavisitingacademicat(2008)theGeologyDepartmentofIndianaUniversityand(2011)theDepartmentofEarthandPlanetaryScience,UniversityofCalifornia,Berkeley.
&nbsp;
ThekeyareasofDr.He&rsquo;sresearcharebasinstructureandpetroleumaccumulation,marinepetroleumandmine,newmaritimeindustries,andgeologicalhazards.
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Achievementsinresearchandindustry:
&nbsp;
1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(in2004-2010)Aschiefdirector,ledpetroleumexplorationprojectsinNorthwestChina,builtstructuralmodelsofTarim,Jungar,QaidamandJiuquanbasins,andwasresponsibleforseveralmajoroil/gasdiscoveriesinTarimandJungarbasins.
&nbsp;
2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(in2009-2012)BuiltstructuralsuperpositionmodelsandpetroleumaccumulationpatternsinXihuTrough(EastChinaSea),predictedtheexistenceoflargeandmedium-sizedoil-gasfieldsaroundXihuTroughbasedontheregionalhydrocarbonsourceconditions,andwasfirsttochartthegeographicaldistributionsofthemajoroil-gasfieldsinareasgeologicallyrelatedtothecoal-bearingPinghuFormation.
&nbsp;
3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(in1998-2003)Builtasystemdynamicmodelforpetroleumgeneration,expulsion,migration,accumulationanddispersion,wroteandproducedprogramsmodellingoil/gasformation,anddeterminedthedistributionofpetroleumsystemofZhuâ…¢depressionoftheSouthChinaSea.
&nbsp;
4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(in2008)Awardeeofthe&ldquo;NationwideTop100MostInfluentialAcademicResearchArticlesoftheYear&rdquo;,bytheChineseMinistryofScienceandTechnology,
Article:He,Y.G.etal(2008)&ldquo;TheMesozoicPrototypeofQuakeDepressionofTarimBasin&rdquo;ChineseJournalofGeology[Chinese]41:44&ndash;53.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(in2010)SecondPrizeforScientificandTechnologicalAdvancementsfromZhejiangProvinceofChina.
&nbsp;
6.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(in2009-2011)Editor-in-chiefof&ldquo;DevelopmentalPlanningGuidelines(2012&ndash;2020)forNewCompetitiveMaritimeIndustrialSectorsandOtherEmergingSectorsoftheZhoushanArchipelago(Zhejiang,China)&rdquo;.&nbsp;ThisregionaldevelopmentproposalwasapprovedandstronglysupportedbytheChineseStateCouncil.
&nbsp;
&nbsp;Ithasbecomethedevelopmentalguideofmarine-relatedemergingindustrialsectorsofZhoushancityandZhejiangProvinceforitsclarity,high-aiming,big-thinking(bigprojectssupportedbybigplatformsforbigsectors),goodprospectsfordevelopment,largedriveandstrongfeasibility.
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
			
				
